# Keep this directory tracked, but never commit raw extension config dumps
# that may contain secrets. Commit a sanitized version per file instead.
#
# To track a sanitized version:
#   1. Strip secrets (e.g. jq 'del(.exaApiKey,.geminiApiKey)' < src > dst)
#   2. git add -f pi-config/extensions/<name>.json
#
# Default: ignore everything except this gitignore and explicitly-added files.
*
!.gitignore
